ad93c895f844738e46134b8867cd0c3fe9d84b61b72dc2e697567a47e7b92f9a15be2a9d5194a7351242e929b98958dc537430b42e030452445991b80dbeaf35  0001-setup-disk-dont-try-install-syslinux-on-unsupported-.patch"
